Using Vosk audio -> text
1. convert to wav:
ffmpeg -i file.m4b -ar 16000 -ac 1 file.wav
2. navigate to vosk-api/python/example/
python3 ./test_simple.py file.wav
3. this generates a dictated.json file to the desktop. That can be search/filtered and the timestamps can be used.

For use with chapter metadata
https://ffmpeg.org/ffmpeg-formats.html#Metadata-1

